title: Starky's Authentic Americana
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Bakery, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Family-owned restaurant offering several vegetarian dishes and a daily vegetarian special. In 2015 it began offering a vegan reuben sandwich (not on menu, ask for it), and during the holidays a "vegan gobbler" -- both using house-made seitan and bread, vegan mayo.
